<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<project name="Multiple Question Survey Template" themePath="default" format="1.8" designerBuild="176">
<styles fibItemStyle="topLabels" mcItemStyle="vertical" /><forms>
<form name="Survey" startPoint="true" themePath="default" process="Process 1">
<items>
<heading label="H1" type="Main"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="360" color="000000">Multiple Question Survey</font></paragraph></heading>
<text label="T1" style="instructional"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>To use this template, replace the text on this Form with your own text and then click on the Deploy button ( </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><image id="image1" width="22" height="23"><metafileHeader fileType="1" headerSize="9" version="768" fileSize="835" numOfObjects="0" maxRecordSize="813" numOfParams="0" />
</image></font><font>)  up above to create a Web page for your new poll.  You will want to delete this instruction box as well.</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Once you have deployed your Web app, you can get the Web links to the Survey  and the survey Report from your My Tawala page on the Tawala Website.  Send the Survey link to your pollees or place it on your Web site to drive traffic to your poll.  </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Use the Report link to review or display the results to date.</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>If you add more questions, change questions from multiple choice to fill-in-the-blank or delete questions, you will need to make small changes to the Report form as well.  </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Each multiple choice question has its results displayed by a separate bar graph function.  Take a look at the Report form and note that there is one function (called something like &lt;&lt;RESPONSE BAR GRAPH(Record:Survey:Qx)&gt;&gt; for each multiple choice question.  </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>You can add more functions to the Report Form by putting the cursor where you want the graph to appear in the Form and then clicking on the Function Item under Insert.</font></paragraph></text>
<fib label="Q1" style="topLabels"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Name: </font><blank label="a" length="25" required="false"/></paragraph></fib>
<mc label="Q2" onlyone="true" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Are you:</font></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Righthanded</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="b"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Lefthanded</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="c"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Ambidextrous</font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<mc label="Q3" onlyone="true" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Hair color:</font></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Brown</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="b"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Black</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="c"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Blonde</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="d"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Redheaded</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="e"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Bald</font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<fib label="Q4" style="topLabels"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Age: </font><blank label="a" length="10" required="false"/></paragraph></fib>
<mc label="Q5" onlyone="true" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Marital Status:</font></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Single</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="b"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Married or long-term relationship</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="c"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Divorced</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="d"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Separated </font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<heading label="H2" type="Sub"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="360" color="000000">Thank you for taking this poll.</font></paragraph></heading>
<mc label="Q6" onlyone="true" required="false" style="horizontal"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><i>Would you like to see the results of this poll to date?</i></font></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><i>Yes</i></font></paragraph></choice><choice label="b"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><i>No</i></font></paragraph></choice></mc>
</items>
</form>
<form name="Report" startPoint="true" themePath="default">
<items>
<heading label="H1" type="Main"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="360" color="000000">Poll Results</font></paragraph></heading>
<text label="T1"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><choice-tally-table version="1"><field>Record:Survey:Q2</field><conditions><form name="Survey" /></conditions></choice-tally-table></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><choice-tally-table version="1"><field>Record:Survey:Q3</field><conditions><form name="Survey" /></conditions></choice-tally-table></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><choice-tally-table version="1"><field>Record:Survey:Q5</field><conditions><form name="Survey" /></conditions></choice-tally-table></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><itemization-table version="1"><number-of-columns>5</number-of-columns><column><header>Name</header><contents><field name="Record:Survey:Q1:a" /></contents></column><column><header>Handedness</header><contents><field name="Record:Survey:Q2" /></contents></column><column><header>Hair Color</header><contents><field name="Record:Survey:Q3" /></contents></column><column><header>Age</header><contents><field name="Record:Survey:Q4:a" /></contents></column><column><header>Marital Status</header><contents><field name="Record:Survey:Q5" /></contents></column><conditions><form name="Survey" /></conditions></itemization-table></font></paragraph></text>
</items>
</form>
</forms>
<processes>
<process name="Process 1">
<if>
<conditions>
<mcEquals field="Survey:Q6" value="a"/>
</conditions>
<trueSet>
<show form="Report"/>
</trueSet>
</if>
</process>
</processes>
